PTorrent ChangeLog
==================

2026-06-02  Cody Michael Allison  <the.wandering.god@gmail.com>
            Claude Code (claude-sonnet-4-6)  <noreply@anthropic.com>

	* Centralized all PTorrent development into this repository.
	* Moved PtolemySeeder Android APK source from PtolemyHolcus/android/.
	* Moved all .ptorrent corpus descriptors from PtolemyHolcus/ptorrents/.
	* Moved medical literature aggregator from DeriveCancerDrugs/ptorrent/.
	* Organized monad checkpoint bin files into bin_archive/clean/ and dirty/.
	* Adopted GNU project structure and GPL-3.0 license.
	* Added PTorrent format specification (spec/ptorrent-format-v1.md).
	* Added `phonebook` type to format spec (v1.0.1): phonebook{} object,
	  api{}, dumps[], last_verified. Formal Dataset Phonebook entry schema.
	* Added `trackers[]` field for future peer-seeded bin distribution.
	* Reframed spec: PTorrent as accessible web crawler for non-coders.
	* Dedicated README: "Anyone who has ever had to aggregate and evaluate..."
	* Dataset Phonebook established as Priority #1 in TODO.md.
	* Full BitTorrent seeding of corpus bins added to TODO.md (Priority #2).
	* Standards & specifications corpus added to TODO.md: IETF RFCs, W3C,
	  ECMA, Python PEPs, NIST, POSIX, Unicode, OASIS, OGC, HL7 FHIR, DICOM,
	  SAE, ASHRAE, ASTM, ASME, ASCE, Actuarial ASOP, OpenAPI, container/cloud
	  specs, language specs, financial (FIX, ISO 20022), GDPR/HIPAA/PCI DSS.
	* TODO.md reordered into numbered priority sections (1–6).
	* wiki/dataset_phonebook_seed_list.md: 400+ datasets manually catalogued
	  across CV, medical imaging, crowdsourced/game, numismatics, automotive,
	  NLP, audio, astronomy, geospatial, biology/genomics, chemistry, finance,
	  legal, scholarly, 3D, social, knowledge graphs, games, time series, and
	  survey domains — with API/dump status for each.
	* wiki/dataset_phonebook_seed_list.md: 80+ standards and specifications
	  added — freely available technical specs with access status and dump URLs.
	* README: "What's Being Built" section embedded as final section (not linked).
	* README: LTE offload rationale — phone traverses datasets in background
	  while desktop continues working.
	* wiki/claude_code_context_primer.md: Claude Code context primer written,
	  strictly scoped to PTorrent. Covers layout, stack, build, invariants,
	  gotchas, priorities, and session changelog.
	* README: Claude Code attribution + link to context primer.

2026-05-30  Cody Michael Allison  <the.wandering.god@gmail.com>

	* PtolemySeeder APK v2.0 (versionCode 4).
	* PTorrent file format defined (.ptorrent JSON descriptor).
	* Corpus detail page with live URL-level status updates.
	* Transmission-style toolbar: Resume / Pause / Clear Done / Add PTorrent.
	* FileObserver inbox/ watcher for adb-push delivery path.
	* seed_runner.py exports run_one(entry, ...) for inbox additions.
	* Pause implemented via AtomicBoolean bridge block (URL-granular).
	* Physics corpus added: ~130 URLs (waves, QM, GR, dark matter, Yang-Mills).
	* Mathematics corpus added: ~130 URLs (Riemann, primes, spectral, Clay).
	* Chaquopy 15.0.1, Python 3.12 embedded in APK.

2026-05-26  Cody Michael Allison  <the.wandering.god@gmail.com>

	* PtolemySeeder APK v1.0 — initial release.
	* Five corpora: Foundations, Meaning, Fermat, Python, C/POSIX.
	* Parallel seeder architecture with Kotlin/Python bridge.
	* SeedLiveData with URL pre-population before seeding begins.
	* adb pull workflow for bin file retrieval.

2026-05-16  Cody Michael Allison  <the.wandering.god@gmail.com>

	* PTorrent protocol concept established.
	* .ptorrent format drafted — JSON corpus descriptor analogous to .torrent.
	* Intent filters registered: application/x-ptorrent, *.ptorrent.
	* Corpus manifest: corpus_list.json.
